These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: ivory, brown
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, bolivar
1. the bongani-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is not the person who likes brown##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | brown   | ivory  |
| Sport   | bongani | bolivar |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, soccer
City: nizza, paris
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is not the person who's sport is soccer##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | surfing | soccer      |
| Pet    | nizza  | paris |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
